{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe6d9dc5fe","title":"不论新区、老区均须召开县的各界代表会议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"20952d9573","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":25,"articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"38b0159818","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的给华中局等的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"07a0cddf30","type":"title","text":"不论新区、老区均须召开县的各界代表会议！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe"},{"id":"38b0159818","type":"paragraph","text":"华中局，并告东北局、华北局、华东局、西北局、山东分局、华南分局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe"},{"id":"09070b4306","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）八月二十日电悉。望将各城各界人民代表会经验抗要电告。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe"},{"id":"48c16eb2d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）务须催促各城开会每月至少一次。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe"},{"id":"08b848e742","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）各县应开县各界代表会议，由农会、工会、学生会、文化教育界、工商业界及党政军，选派代表，可以选择若干开明绅士参加，讨论全县工作。大县代表二百余人，中县代表一百余人，小县代表数十人。每月或每两月开会一次，每次两天至三天开完。此事华东、华中、西北、南方各新区均可做。各老解放区更不待说。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe"},{"id":"33b8d63439","type":"subtitle","text":"中央未有","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe"}],"page":{"id":"053da25923","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fe6d9dc5fe","start":169,"end":169}}}},"__N_SSG":true}